                                            "Text": {
                                                "val": "FY19 RDTE of $8M was utilized to execute the following actions:\n  -AVIS development included hardware enhancements by adding additional driver cameras, enhancing the license plate camera field of view, and upgrading the vehicle detection\/trigger.  \n  -KBII development included development of the KBII Geolock and Watchbox hardware capabilities. \n  -IRIS-G integration included hardware and software upgrades to be integrated into the three systems. This included the initial development for the JACCS integration."
